=========== Theme setup ===========================
NEW LAYOUT SETUP POINTS

- color scheme setup (globally)
- font family setup as per logo (globally)
Header points.
- logo update
- fav icon logo update
- mega menu setup
- search filed add 
- admin icon add
Main page.
- Add H1 tag atleast one time on home page
- banner with Image slide + add vedio on slider
- show best collection
- show feature product with all options
    (like swatch , subscriptions etc) 
- vedio sections added ( with diffrent style)
- newslatter sections 
- show product review badges ( free app product review)
Footer points.
- show payment icon
- copyright text
- show privacy page in footer 
- social icon 
Collection page points.
- show filters ( free app search & discovery)
- show sorting system
- show breadcrumbs
- show 2nd image on hover
- show quick view options 
- show add to cart
Product page points.
- show breadcrumbs
- Image gallery with thumbnails
- zoom options
- video acceptable in product gallery
- product review
- show swatch color 
- buy now button add
- short descriipition
- customer review comment sections 
- share button 
- side cart show on click add to cart button


Checkout page points.
- logo update
- one page checkout or step form checkout

Cart page points.
- add note field 
-


Extra points.
- check site fully responsive
- make all heading same font size 
- compressed Image used 


